<i>noun</i>: 확산 [확싼], 이산 [이ː산], 분산 [분산] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확산 [확싼]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spread; dispersion; diffusion; proliferation</dd><br>
<dd>흩어져 널리 퍼짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of scattering and spreading out.</dd><br>
<dd>2. diffusion</dd><br>
<dd>서로 농도가 다른 물질을 섞었을 때, 시간이 지나면서 조금씩 농도가 같아지는 현상.</dd><br>
<dd>A phenomenon in which substances with different levels of concentrations gradually reach the same level of concetration over time when they are mixed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이산 [이ː산]</dt><br>
<dd>separation; dispersion</dd><br>
<dd>헤어지거나 이별하여 흩어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being dispersed due to a parting or separation.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>분산 [분산]</dt><br>
<dd>dispersion</dd><br>
<dd>갈라져 흩어짐. 또는 그렇게 되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>Things or people being dispersed; the act of dispersing things or people.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>